{"title":"WTC Adds New Tubeless Valve Stem Kits to the Color Shop","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-tubeless-valve-stem-kits-color-shop/","date":1712327760000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-tooth-components-tubeless-valves-all-colors-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Wolf tooth components tubeless valves all colors\" /></p>\n<p>Yup, the color wheel keeps on spinnin’. Over at the Wolf Tooth Components HQ, they just added <a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/products/tubeless-valve-stem-kit?variant=40270036500515\" target=\"_blank\">Tubeless Valve Stem Kits</a> to the Color Shop. The new WTC Tubeless Valves are now available in 9 colors to help with your steed’s matchy-matchy vibe (there’s also black and silver). </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-purple-e1712262138995.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"936\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-purple-e1712262138995.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components New Tubeless Valve Stem purple\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-purple-e1712262138995.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-purple-e1712262138995-297x217.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-purple-e1712262138995-120x88.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-purple-e1712262138995-768x562.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/Wolf Tooth Components)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Valve Stems are also available in two sizes, either 44mm or 60mm lengths to fit most MTB, Road, and Fat wheels. They include a core remover cap, extra cores, gaskets, and a custom nut for solid and easy installation. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components New Tubeless Valve Stem red mounted\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-mounted-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There are also three different rubber base options included, so you can find the best fit for your particular rim’s internal shape.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Wolf Tooth Valve Stem Features and Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $31.95</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>44mm and 60mm stem length options</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Slotted stem base for compatibility with tire inserts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Oversized stem nut for better sealing and easier removal</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stem threaded below rubber seal for better performance on single-wall rims</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Three rubber bases included: two types of cones (one installed), one channel</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Replacement parts available via Wolf Tooth Right To Repair, including cap kit with  two caps, nut kit with two nuts, and valve cores</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313.jpeg\"><img width=\"1006\" height=\"670\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313.jpeg\" alt=\"Wolf Tooth Components New Tubeless Valve Stem red matchy match\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313.jpeg 1006w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313-768x511.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Wolf-Tooth-Components-New-Tubeless-Valve-Stem-red-matchy-match-e1712262246313-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The available colors are black, blue, gold, oil slick, orange, pink, purple, raw silver, and red. Click the link below to have fun getting your color on. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WolfToothComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wtc-tubeless-valve-stem-kits-color-shop/\">WTC Adds New Tubeless Valve Stem Kits to the Color Shop</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"caacf345cd36824972d80c01805c16dffe5423f0ca918c5f38b10ade5e13f0fa","category":"Cycling"}